WEBVTT

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:03.390
Whenever I ask this question, 
women remember those clothes.

00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:07.350
Possibly, even you would be remembering.

00:03:07.640 --> 00:03:10.550
I myself have not forgotten
my school uniform.

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:15.680
When women and girls 
are repeatedly warned and taught fear,

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:18.900
they are also told that 
their safety is their responsibility.

00:03:18.900 --> 00:03:21.990
And if any sexual violence takes place, 
like it does every day,

00:03:21.990 --> 00:03:24.530
it is their fault;
they could have been more careful.

00:03:24.530 --> 00:03:26.700
Not just at home, even politicians,

00:03:26.700 --> 00:03:29.260
police, village headmen, 
lawyers in public service

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:32.190
have blamed women 
for the violence they are facing.